係windows關機之後唔係完全可以熄到機<br />\n嗰啲顯卡風扇電源燈keep住著<br />\n最後要係親手㩒實電源制先熄到<br />\n單獨換cpu換板都係咁<br />\n之後換咗後備嘅r5 1600同gigabyte ab350m就冇事 開十次十次都冇問題<br />\n就咁睇好似係cpu同塊板嘅問題<br />\n然後拎咗嗰兩件嘢翻去買嗰間舖到測試<br />\n佢哋又開到機試唔出有咩事<br />\n<br />\n求各位巴打幫幫小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T13:11:14.000Z","msg":"1. 電源選項＞選擇按下電源按鈕時的行為＞關閉快速啟動<br />\n<br />\n2. 電源選擇＞變更計劃設定＞變更進階電源＞睡眠＞關閉混合式睡眠。<br />\n<br />\n3. 再唔係手動關機＞開始 , cmd,  shutdown -s -t 10=&gt;"},{"pid":"7d54deacfab6e2558abb139a198c7dbdda9ef58a","tid":2353404,"uid":219274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"993f192d26e4ca495be6e550686a73f9c3b0507f","tid":2353404,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20260f8486711461f1855369e63b9ea5c22822ee","tid":2353404,"uid":219274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3a62a6ff1a2a6b6933b1b90531dc63729859d23","tid":2353404,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T12:55:12.000Z","msg":"有冇UPDATE BIOS"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n最新嗰個<br />\n但未update前已經有陣時係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T13:04:25.000Z","msg":"有冇用1600落塊B450度試"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T14:18:11.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n係成功熄到機<br />\n但熄之前彈咗句咩read error之後就開唔到"},{"pid":"b92d9ead27407caf32058bffb566ee8d02aad6c6","tid":2353404,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d54deacfab6e2558abb139a198c7dbdda9ef58a","tid":2353404,"uid":219274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"993f192d26e4ca495be6e550686a73f9c3b0507f","tid":2353404,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20260f8486711461f1855369e63b9ea5c22822ee","tid":2353404,"uid":219274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n最新嗰個<br />\n但未update前已經有陣時係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces